Package: senateaR
Title: Access Open Data from the Argentine Senate
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Vinicius", "Santos", email = "santos.vinicius18@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to fetch and parse open data published by the
    Argentine Senate ("Senado de la Nacion Argentina"), including current and
    historical senators, voting records and vote details, commissions,
    session bulletins, procurement notices ("licitaciones"), parliamentary
    entries ("asuntos entrados"), and stenographic transcripts. Data are
    retrieved directly from the Senate's public open-data portal and website.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/vsntos/senateaR
BugReports: https://github.com/vsntos/senateaR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
